<doc id="1006462" wikidata="Q6826413" url="?curid=1006462" title="Meyer Dolinsky">
<text>Meyer Dolinsky (October 13, 1923 in Chicago, Illinois – February 29, 1984 in Los Angeles, California), aka Mike Dolinsky (sometimes credited as &quot;Michael Adams&quot; or &quot;Mike Adams&quot;), was an American screenwriter. Before transitioning to the screen, he wrote radio scripts.

