Director: James Sheldon &lt;br&gt;
Screenwriter: Rod Serling &lt;br&gt;
Starring: Gary Merrill (Paradine), Vaughn Taylor (Old Man), Ben Cooper (Dauger), Addison Myers (Sentry); Mark Tapscott (Lieutenant), Jack Mann (Mallory)

