Adapted for television for Night Gallery, aired 27 October 1971 &lt;br&gt;
Director: Gene Kearney &lt;br&gt;
Screenwriter: Gene Kearney &lt;br&gt;
Starring: Helmut Dantine (General), Francis Lederer (Master), Hank Brandt (Kranz)

